libsigsegv: libsigsegv (handling page faults in user mode)
libsigsegv:
libsigsegv: This is a library for handling page faults in user mode. 
libsigsegv: A page fault occurs when a program tries to access to a 
libsigsegv: region of memory that is currently not available.
libsigsegv: 
libsigsegv: 
